            <p class="section-bundle-service__description">{% if request.locale.iso_code == 'sv' %}Professionella handskar och skydd — inga junioranpassningar.{% else %}Pro-grade gloves and protection — no junior downgrades.{% endif %}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section-bundle-service__item">
            <img class="section-bundle-service__image" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0667/5877/0944/files/3_edd68857-f789-4d4a-81cb-fbf0240abe20.png?v=1750500636" alt="service" />
            <p class="section-bundle-service__caption">{% if request.locale.iso_code == 'sv' %}24 timmars leverans{% else %}24 Hour Dispatch{% endif %}</p>
