        </div>
        <div class="section-bundle-service__item">
            <img class="section-bundle-service__image" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0667/5877/0944/files/4.png?v=1750500637" alt="service" />
            <p class="section-bundle-service__caption">{% if request.locale.iso_code == 'sv' %}Gratis & smidiga storleksbyten{% else %}Free & Easy Size Exchanges{% endif %}</p>
            <p class="section-bundle-service__description">{% if request.locale.iso_code == 'sv' %}Snabba & enkla byten om storleken inte passar{% else %}Quick & simple swaps if your sizing isn’t right.{% endif %}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section-bundle-service__item">
            <img class="section-bundle-service__image" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0667/5877/0944/files/5_7b09bad5-a924-403e-9484-aeda5b3443b7.png?v=1750500636" alt="service" />
            <p class="section-bundle-service__caption">{% if request.locale.iso_code == 'sv' %}Ett paket. Hela säsongen fixad.{% else %}One Bundle. Full Season Sorted.{% endif %}</p>
            <p class="section-bundle-service__description">{% if request.locale.iso_code == 'sv' %}Handskar, vadderad utrustning och tillbehör — inga blandade märken.{% else %}Gloves, padded kit & accessory — no mixing brands.{% endif %}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section-bundle-service__item">
            <img class="section-bundle-service__image" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0667/5877/0944/files/6_32975205-8eb9-4d0d-9bee-49e74c24cda3.png?v=1750500637" alt="service" />
            <p class="section-bundle-service__caption">{% if request.locale.iso_code == 'sv' %}10-matchers garanti{% else %}10-Game Guarantee{% endif %}</p>
            <p class="section-bundle-service__description">{% if request.locale.iso_code == 'sv' %}Om dina handskar inte lever upp till förväntningarna — byter vi ut dem.{% else %}If your gloves don’t deliver — we replace them.{% endif %}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-bundle-service__wrap">
        <a class="section-bundle-service__button" href="#build-bundle-product">{% if request.locale.iso_code == 'sv' %}BYGG DERAS PAKET →{% else %}BUILD THEIR BUNDLE →{% endif %}</a>
        <p class="section-bundle-service__text">
            <img src="{{ 'verified_black.svg' | asset_url }}" alt="arrow" />
            {% if request.locale.iso_code == 'sv' %}10-matchers garanti{% else %}10 Game Guarantee{% endif %}
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

